{"tid":489291,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"點解冇人講野境WILDLAND 4VS4?","createTime":"2017-12-04T14:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T03:40:30.000Z","uid":106042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b4db01eedf09596f7254f84f3bd57317d9e60f1f","tid":489291,"uid":106042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:02:24.000Z","msg":"我明 呢隻GAME又係大家唔太睇好既UB出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當初玩都係買黎陪朋友玩下<br />\n單機真係唔太吸引...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nanyway 自從佢出左4vs4之後 <br />\n真係停唔到 日日都玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主要係佢玩法真係好吸引我 係其他game比唔到<br />\n佢玩法就好似打war game咁<br />\n<br />\n可能大部分時間要係草叢埋伏 要聽聲 同睇情報<br />\n當然都有兵種係戰鬥型 偵測人員 軍醫<br />\n混合十幾個兵種 各種唔同技能 <br />\n發揮出唔同既戰略攻勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為可以救人返生既關係 仲有唔多唔少既兵種剋制<br />\n有時1vs4都可以打得好刺激 反敗為勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而且最重要係討厭課金既我 <br />\n打wild 4vs4都唔會出現rainbow six/ battlefield既不公平場面 <br />\n或者花大量時間練兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入game方面 絕冇死場 平均30-1分鐘就load完入場<br />\n打得好爽快 如果撞正4個都開mic打就一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講左咁耐 如果你手頭上有呢隻game<br />\n希望你地唔好放棄佢 pvp係唔駛比錢dl既<br />\n得閒就開黎玩下 同單機版真係唔同game黎"},{"pid":"d6f8b3e6bb0cbd3eda691b1f2f5c5d05b1795fa4","tid":489291,"uid":106042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:23:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7a688630d402e5c18626a04193499481a6e8a3a5","tid":489291,"uid":35043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT